title: Parochials and Groups 3-4-5 polls
text: Parochials and Groups 3-4-5 polls Pat PJR Rice Talk about it in NJHoops Hardwood Talk I made some changes, including one team I thought was underrated. If you don't like where your school is placed or not placed, you will have plenty of time to prove me wrong. I am currently placing any team with an undefeated record with a minimum of "knocking on the door." Parochials: 1 - St. Joe's, Montvale (5-2)2 - Bergen Catholic (4-2) 4 - St. Peter's Prep (4-2)5 - Paramus Catholic (3-3)
